datasets.name: 39a5402c
datasets.query:
-- CTE to get the top 5 topics by the number of tickets
WITH TopTopics AS (
  SELECT topic
  FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_customer_support.customer_support_review
  GROUP BY topic
  ORDER BY COUNT(ticket_id) DESC
  LIMIT 5
),
-- CTE to get the top 4 countries by the number of tickets
TopCountries AS (
  SELECT country
  FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_customer_support.customer_support_review
  GROUP BY country
  ORDER BY COUNT(ticket_id) DESC
  LIMIT 4
)

-- Main query to select data from the technical support dataset
SELECT 
       *,
       -- Calculate the resolution time in hours, adding a random adjustment for Tier 2 support level
       (TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, created_time, resolution_time) 
              + CASE 
           WHEN support_level = 'Tier 2' THEN FLOOR(3000 + (RAND() * (3000 - 2400)))
           ELSE 0 
         END) / 60.0 AS adjusted_resolution_time
FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_customer_support.customer_support_review
-- Filter to include only tickets with top topics
WHERE topic IN (SELECT topic FROM TopTopics)
-- Filter to include only tickets from top countries
AND country IN (SELECT country FROM TopCountries)
-- Exclude tickets where the resolution time is zero
AND TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, created_time, resolution_time) != 0;

datasets.name: 916033f4
datasets.query:
SELECT country, COUNT(ticket_id) AS support_volume
FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_customer_support.customer_support_review
GROUP BY country

datasets.name: 44cccafd
datasets.query:
SELECT topic, COUNT(ticket_id) AS support_volume, 
       (COUNT(ticket_id) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_customer_support.customer_support_review)) AS percentage
FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_customer_support.customer_support_review
GROUP BY topic

datasets.name: 56d2ee72
datasets.query:
SELECT 
  SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'In progress' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS in_progress_tickets,
  SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'Closed' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS closed_tickets,
  SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'Resolved' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS resolved_tickets
FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_customer_support.customer_support_review
